25:02.734 --> 25:04.202
might be worth a try.

25:04.202 --> 25:07.005
It is true nothing makes
your father happier

25:07.005 --> 25:09.441
than seeing the effect
he has on you.

25:15.180 --> 25:17.616
It's five minutes till, so...

25:17.616 --> 25:19.885
