According to
Detective Lenz's report...

27:06.091 --> 27:07.592
...24 were not hits,

27:07.592 --> 27:09.361
meaning those prints
belonged to individuals

27:09.361 --> 27:10.962
who are not in the system.

27:10.962 --> 27:13.498
But ten prints did match
with one individual.

27:13.498 --> 27:15.000
The defendant.

27:15.000 --> 27:18.203
...denied ever having been
inside Ms. Forrest's apartment.

27:18.203 --> 27:20.972
H-He also denied ever having
a personal relationship

27:20.972 --> 27:22.641
with Ms. Forrest. However, upon

27:22.641 --> 27:24.810
subsequent interviews
with other parties...

27:24.810 --> 27:26.278
I saw her wink at someone,

27:26.278 --> 27:28.113
and when I looked to see who,

27:28.113 --> 27:29.648
I saw it was Dan Gallagher.

27:29.648 --> 27:32.551
And then Ms. Forrest
motioned to Mr. Gallagher,

27:32.551 --> 27:34.486
like to tell him
that he had something,

27:34.486 --> 27:36.388
some-some food on his face
or something.

27:36.388 --> 27:38.023
After a short conversation,

27:38.023 --> 27:40.425
I then used the restroom,
and when I returned,

27:40.425 --> 27:43.028
I noted both the defendant
and Ms. Forrest

27:43.028 --> 27:44.629
had left the premises.

27:44.629 --> 27:47.365
I next attempted to speak
to a, uh, Mr. Rodney Scanlon,

27:47.365 --> 27:50.535
who works as the head bartender
at Andolini's Restaurant.

27:50.535 --> 27:52.237
I don't recall.

27:52.237 --> 27:54.473
Did you ever see the defendant

27:54.473 --> 27:57.175
in Andolini's with Ms. Forrest?

27:57.175 --> 27:58.577
I don't recall.

27:58.577 --> 28:00.378
Have you ever heard

28:00.378 --> 28:02.180
