and Ms. Forrest

28:02.180 --> 28:03.882
were involved
in a personal relationship?

28:03.882 --> 28:05.784
I don't recall.

28:05.784 --> 28:08.753
He subsequently came
to my office to request

28:08.753 --> 28:10.555
