someone else do for him,

28:17.662 --> 28:19.331
or done over the phone.

28:19.331 --> 28:21.433
The defense has indicated that

28:21.433 --> 28:24.202
Ms. Forrest struggled with...

28:24.202 --> 28:27.105
That she was, in their words,

28:27.105 --> 28:29.140
unstable.

28:29.941 --> 28:32.277
Did you ever see any signs

28:32.277 --> 28:33.778
of instability?

28:33.778 --> 28:37.415
No. Our job is very stressful, psychologically,

28:37.415 --> 28:40.785
so I-I try to watch
for the effects of that,

28:40.785 --> 28:42.287
manage for them.

28:42.287 --> 28:44.289
Alex never confided in me

28:44.289 --> 28:46.091
that she was struggling
in any way,

28:46.091 --> 28:47.993
and I never saw
any sign of it in her.

28:47.993 --> 28:50.662
I saw a caring
and dedicated advocate.

28:52.364 --> 28:54.666
One of the best we ever had.

28:55.734 --> 28:58.136
Have you talked to him about it?

28:58.136 --> 29:00.171
