for right now,

29:02.674 --> 29:04.476
let's try to honor

29:04.476 --> 29:06.311
this decision
with an explanation

29:06.311 --> 29:08.179
before you make it.

29:08.179 --> 29:10.482
What are you looking for
with this move?

29:10.482 --> 29:13.151
What other ways
