30:21.653 --> 30:24.222
<i>You have any idea
what that was like?</i>

30:24.222 --> 30:26.891
<i>Getting laughed at
by this asshole because</i>

30:26.891 --> 30:29.861
<i>I don't know
my own fucking daughter moved?</i>

30:29.861 --> 30:31.696
<i>Or where she went?</i>

30:31.696 --> 30:33.565
<i>I should call the cops
and report you missing.</i>

30:33.565 --> 30:35.934
<i>Tell them
you're a danger to yourself.</i>

30:35.934 --> 30:38.403
<i>That's what you deserve.</i>

30:38.403 --> 30:40.105
<i>You expect people
to care about you</i>

30:40.105 --> 30:41.673
<i>when you treat them like this?</i>

30:41.673 --> 30:43.842
<i>Not to mention,
